{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 155221,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ガイはシルキィに語りかけます」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Gai speaks to Silky.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155222,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「面白い娘だ、魔人となり私の部下となれ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You're an interesting girl; become a demon and my subordinate.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155223,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「なるほど、それでシルキィは",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I see, so that’s why Silky..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155224,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　晴れて魔人の仲間入りしたってわけか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "…officially joined the ranks of the demons.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155225,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いえ、まだ続きがあります。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, there’s more."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155226,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　この話の最も大事なポイントです」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "This is the most important point of this story.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155227,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「逆に、瀕死の状態にも関わらず、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"On the contrary, despite being on the brink of death,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155228,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　シルキィは魔王ガイに条件を出しました」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Silky gave Demon Lord Gai a condition.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155229,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「私を部下にしたいのなら、人類から手を引け。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If you want me as your subordinate, withdraw from humanity."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155230,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それが条件だ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That is the condition.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155231,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「――と」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"—And so.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155232,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「これを受け、その四年後、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Accepting this, four years later,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155233,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　本当にガイは人類から手を引きました」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Gai truly withdrew from humanity.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155234,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「今の世界の魔物界と人間界の境界線は",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The current boundary between the monster world and the human world"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155235,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　このときに作られたものです」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "was created at this time.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155236,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「人類が魔物から解放されたのは、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Humanity’s liberation from monsters"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155237,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　彼女たった一人のおかげということです」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "is thanks to this one woman alone.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155238,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ほほーう、英雄ってのはそういうことか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oh ho, so that’s what a hero is all about.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155239,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔人となったシルキィは、魔人として、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Silky, having become a demon, as a demon,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155240,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ガイの部下として力をつけました」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "gained strength as Gai’s subordinate.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155241,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「人間だった頃からは考えられないほど、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"To an unimaginable extent compared to when she was human,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155242,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　高度、かつ強力な魔導具を作り、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "she created advanced and powerful magical devices,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155243,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔人四天王の一角にまで上り詰めます」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "rising to become one of the Four Heavenly Kings of the demons.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155244,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「その後はご存じのように、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"After that, as you know,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155245,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　派閥戦争でホーネット派の一員として、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "she fought on the front lines as a member of the Hornet faction during the faction war..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155246,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　常に前線に立ち戦ったとか……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"… always standing on the front lines.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155247,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「彼女はもしかしたら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Perhaps she is,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155248,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　未だ人類の為に戦っているのかも知れない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "still fighting for humanity.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155249,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そう、言われています」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That is what is said.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155250,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "…………",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "………"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155251,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "…"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155252,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「以上がＡＬ教で司教以上に教えられる話です。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That is the story taught to bishops and above in the AL religion."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155253,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ある程度の地位がある方なら一度は",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Anyone with a certain level of status has probably heard it at least once."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155254,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　耳に入れたことのある話ですよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155255,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「と言っても真偽不明の話で、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That said, its truth is uncertain,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155256,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　英雄が人類を裏切ったと考えることも出来ます」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and one could think that the hero betrayed humanity.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155257,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「憚られる話なのでわざわざ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Since it’s a taboo topic,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155258,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　言う人もそうはいませんが」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "not many people deliberately speak of it.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155259,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふーん」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155260,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うお、サテラ、すごい顔してるぞ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Whoa, Satella, you’ve got quite a face on you.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155261,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"……\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155262,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「お前ら人類は……ッ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You humans are...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155263,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "サテラは炎のような怒りをその身にまとわせていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Satella was wrapped in anger like a blazing flame."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155264,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「シルキィが今まで",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Silky, until now,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155265,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どんな気持ちで戦っていたと……ッ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "what feelings was she fighting with...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155266,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「今まで？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Until now?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155267,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ホーネット派とケイブリス派の、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The faction war between the Hornet faction and the Cavebris faction,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155268,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　派閥戦争のことだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"that’s what I mean.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155269,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ホーネット派のほとんどは、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Most of the Hornet faction"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155270,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔王の遺言を守る為に戦ってるにすぎない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "are only fighting to uphold the Demon Lord’s last will.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155271,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「でも、でも、シルキィだけは……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"But, but only Silky..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155272,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あいつだけは人類の為に……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "that one alone was fighting for humanity...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155273,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「人類との不可侵を認めたガイ様の選んだ人なら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If she was chosen by Lord Gai, who recognized the non-aggression pact with humanity,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155274,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　もしかしたら、という細い希望の為に……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "then perhaps for that faint hope...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155275,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それを、お前らは……！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"And you all...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155276,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「サテラはシルキィにずっと言ってた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Satella always told Silky,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155277,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　人類なんて守る価値はないって」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "'Humanity isn’t worth protecting.'\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155278,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「やっぱり……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"After all..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155279,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　間違ってなかったようだな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "it seems I was not wrong.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155280,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そうですね。」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That’s right.\""
    }
  ]
}

